                        <div style="height:220px">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-6" style="text-align:center">
                        <p style="text-align:justify">Poor quality lessons can be detrimental for any learner. From unhealthy posture/technique to demotivation, frustration and even giving up on the instrument altogether. This is the reason why Keys to Teach was created - to support tutors by offering a collection of resources which can help to improve the quality of their lessons and encourage creative teaching in every situation and need.</p>
                        <p style="text-align:justify">These strategies will help pupils build a foundation for their performing career as well as their own strategies or "keys to teach" in the future.</p>
                    </div>
